cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB 

This paper is about a solution for Wikification of large corpora, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR) techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the proposed method involves machine learning (ML) and statistical techniques, which are also relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the use of Wikipedia redirects suggests a potential connection to cs.DB (Databases) as well.
